14. Governance vs Management (Important Exam Question)
Data Governance	Data Management
Directs	Executes
Defines Policies	Implements Policies
Decision Rights	Operational Activities
Oversight	Day-to-Day Management
Business Led	Business + IT

Mnemonic:

Governance = Decide and Control
Management = Do and Operate

